@startuml

actor Admin
actor User
participant System
database DB

== Student Self-Seeding ==
User -> System: Submit own completed courses\n(from_admin = FALSE)
System -> System: Check for conflicts\nwith admin records

alt Conflict found
    System -> User: Warn user - admin record differences\nbut user record takes priority
else No conflict
    System -> DB: Save user record
end

@enduml
